Seqnature Change Log

V1.2 build_new_sequence_from_vcfs.py only
	- Adapt to the new Sanger VCF format used with mouse reference
	  build 38.
	- Replace own reference extraction code with pyfaidx, which is
	  now a required module.
	- Information about het calls is now written to a filename 
	  ending in "_het_calls.log" instead of stderr.
